---
title: PauseAI UK | Campaigns
description: Take action on AI safety. Email your MP, join campaigns, and help build pressure for a global pause.
ogTitle: PauseAI UK | Campaigns
ogDescription: Take action on AI safety. Email your MP, join campaigns, and help build pressure for a global pause.
ogImage: /images/open-graph/open-graph-1200-630.jpg
ogImageWidth: 1200
ogImageHeight: 630
ogUrl: https://pauseai.uk/campaigns/
twitterImage: /images/open-graph/open-graph-1600-840.jpg
navPrefix: "/"
extraCss:
  - /campaigns.css
mainClass: campaigns
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="campaigns-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">UK AI Liability Campaign</p>
      <h1>Hold AI developers liable for severe harm</h1>
      <p class="lede">We&rsquo;re calling on the UK government to introduce legislation that makes AI companies legally responsible when their models enable critical harms &mdash; from cyber attacks on national infrastructure to biosecurity threats.</p>
      <p class="hero-cta-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="#email-your-mp">Email your MP &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="campaigns-context">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote>
        AI developers face no meaningful financial or other punitive consequences for foreseeable harms to British citizens.
        <cite>&mdash; Open letter to the Prime Minister</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <p>In February 2026, a single operator used commercially available AI to breach nine Mexican government agencies and exfiltrate the personal data of 195 million citizens. The UK&rsquo;s own AI Security Institute has found that today&rsquo;s most advanced models can <em>&ldquo;discover and exploit vulnerabilities autonomously &mdash; tasks that would take human professionals days of work&rdquo;</em>. Britain depends on the same critical infrastructure these tools can now attack.</p>
      <p>Liability is a simple, technology-neutral way to align AI developers&rsquo; incentives with public safety: those who profit from creating catastrophic risk must bear meaningful responsibility when that risk materialises.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="campaigns-docs">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Read the case in full</h2>
      <div class="docs-grid">
        <a class="doc-card" href="/pdfs/AI%20Liability%20Open%20Letter.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          <img src="/pdfs/AI%20Liability%20Open%20Letter.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="doc-meta">
            <p class="doc-kind">Open letter &mdash; June 2026</p>
            <h3>To the Prime Minister</h3>
            <span class="doc-cta">Read the letter &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="doc-card" href="/pdfs/AI%20Liability%20Policy%20Briefing.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          <img src="/pdfs/AI%20Liability%20Policy%20Briefing.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="doc-meta">
            <p class="doc-kind">Policy briefing &mdash; June 2026</p>
            <h3>AI Developer Liability for Severe Harms</h3>
            <span class="doc-cta">Read the briefing &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="email-your-mp" class="campaigns-embed">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Email your MP</h2>
      <div class="embed-frame">
        <iframe
          id="campaigns-embed"
          src="https://pauseai.info/embed/uk-email-mp"
          title="Email your MP &mdash; PauseAI"
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="embed-fallback">
        Having trouble loading the form?
        <a href="https://pauseai.info/uk-email-mp" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open it on pauseai.info &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="campaigns-share">
    <div class="container">
      <button type="button" class="qr-thumb" aria-label="Show QR code larger">
        <img src="/campaigns/campaign-page-qr-code.png" alt="QR code linking to this campaign page" width="180" height="180" loading="lazy" />
        <span>Scan to share this page</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}

{% block extraBody %}
  <div class="qr-lightbox" id="qr-lightbox" aria-hidden="true" role="dialog" aria-label="QR code">
    <button class="qr-lightbox-close" type="button" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
    <img src="/campaigns/campaign-page-qr-code.png" alt="QR code linking to this campaign page" />
  </div>
{% endblock %}

{% block bodyScripts %}
<script>
  (function () {
    const iframe = document.getElementById("campaigns-embed");
    if (!iframe) return;
    window.addEventListener("message", (e) => {
      const data = e.data;
      if (!data || typeof data !== "object") return;
      if (data.type !== "pauseai-embed-resize") return;
      if (typeof data.height !== "number" || !isFinite(data.height)) return;
      iframe.style.height = data.height + "px";
    });
  })();

  (function () {
    const trigger = document.querySelector(".qr-thumb");
    const lb = document.getElementById("qr-lightbox");
    if (!trigger || !lb) return;
    const closeBtn = lb.querySelector(".qr-lightbox-close");
    const open = () => { lb.classList.add("open"); lb.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "false"); };
    const close = () => { lb.classList.remove("open"); lb.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true"); };
    trigger.addEventListener("click", open);
    closeBtn.addEventListener("click", close);
    lb.addEventListener("click", (e) => { if (e.target === lb) close(); });
    document.addEventListener("keydown", (e) => {
      if (e.key === "Escape" && lb.classList.contains("open")) close();
    });
  })();
</script>
{% endblock %}
